const String cm13 = 'One litre of Water';
const String cm14 = 'Boiling time 40–50 min';
const String cm15 = 'Bamboo can be boiled for couple of hours and will be left in the drum for 24 hours to drawn the chemicals';
const String cm16 = 'STEPPING OR BUT END TREATMENT';
const String cm17 = 'In this process, freshly cut bamboo culms of desired length are immersed with their butt ends in a solution of Boric acid: Borax (50:50) of about 10% concentration. The immersion ends should be done up to a length of about 30 cm of the  but-end. The treatment may last for 8 to 12 days.In this process, freshly cut bamboo culms of desired length are immersed with their butt ends in a solution of Boric acid: Borax (50:50)  of about 10% concentration. The immersion ends should be done up to a length of about 30 cm of the but-end. The treatment may last for 8 to 12 days.';
const String cm18 = 'In this process, stirring of the solution is demanded on every day to avoid sedimentation and also add small amount of the boric acid: Borax mixture to make up the uptake loss. This treatment is suitable for using as fencing/support to horticultural plants like banana, etc. as the end comes in constant contact with the ground.';
const String cm19 = 'DIFFUSION SOAKING PROCESS';
const String cm20 = 'For effective penetration, two opposite holes may be drilled in each internodes before immersion of the culms.In order to fasten the simply dipping in cold solution of preservatives, the solution can also be heated. In such case, the total duration for completion of the process is about 3 hours.';
